{"tid":575830,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"不誠實使用電腦罪","createTime":"2018-02-28T12:14:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-28T17:01:10.000Z","uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3de82231c210a0e9d90bdfd6753ad5a959d4c5e8","tid":575830,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T12:14:49.000Z","msg":"電腦定義<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.infosec.gov.hk/tc_chi/crime/what_crc_1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.infosec.gov.hk%2Ftc_chi%2Fcrime%2Fwhat_crc_1.html&d=g96y2tAFGhmrj%2B%2FMFxWKG9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=3f949501\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.infosec.gov.hk/tc_chi/crime/what_crc_1.html</a><br />\n<br />\n連登好多人吹水<br />\n明明自己無樓話自己有樓<br />\n有樓又話自己住公屋<br />\n<br />\n大學畢業話自己得中學<br />\n讀緊中學又話自己大學畢業<br />\n<br />\n男性扮女性<br />\n女性扮男性<br />\n<br />\n藍絲，紅巴<br />\n<br />\n其實係咪已經觸犯左《不誠實使用電腦罪》？"},{"pid":"6a9b1727c0b14972b9ba043b1bc7bb57b99cf294","tid":575830,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T12:18:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.infosec.gov.hk/tc_chi/ordinances/corresponding.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.infosec.gov.hk%2Ftc_chi%2Fordinances%2Fcorresponding.html&d=g96y2tAFGhmrj%2B%2FMFxWKG9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=9271c52b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.infosec.gov.hk/tc_chi/ordinances/corresponding.html</a><br />\n<br />\n刑事罪行條例<br />\n香港法例第 200章 第 161條<br />\n<br />\n有 犯 罪 <strong>或 不 誠 實 意 圖 </strong>而 取 用 電 腦 ， 可 監 禁 5 年"},{"pid":"f5033056c20ef188d18b82cbed499428bbd32cae","tid":575830,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T12:20:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap200!zh-Hant-HK/s161\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elegislation.gov.hk%2Fhk%2Fcap200%21zh-Hant-HK%2Fs161&d=g96y2tAFGhmrj%2B%2FMFxWKG9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=8b94fa12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap200!zh-Hant-HK/s161</a><br />\n<br />\n第200章 《刑事罪行條例》 ── 第161條 <br />\n<br />\n有犯罪或不誠實意圖而取用電腦<br />\n<br />\n(1)任何人有下述意圖或目的而取用電腦 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(a)意圖犯罪(不論是在取用電腦的同時或在日後任何時間)；<br />\n(b)不誠實地意圖欺騙(不論是在取用電腦的同時或在日後任何時間)；<br />\n(c)目的在於使其本人或他人不誠實地獲益(不論是在取用電腦的同時或在日後任何時間)；或<br />\n(d)不誠實地意圖導致他人蒙受損失(不論是在取用電腦的同時或在日後任何時間)，<br />\n即屬犯罪，一經循公訴程序定罪，可處監禁5年。"},{"pid":"2032049aaa42eeca52a46c6938cade813b0e3d93","tid":575830,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T12:22:57.000Z","msg":"何 謂 電 腦 ?<br />\n<br />\n首 先 ， 我 們 應 加 以 詮 釋 「 電 腦 」 這 個 概 念 。 「 電 腦 」 一 詞 通 常 泛 指 一 台 包 括 顯 示 器 、 鍵 盤 及 中 央 處 理 器 的 獨 立 機 器 。 然 而 ， 隨 著 科 技 不 斷 演 進 ， 「 電 腦 」 一 詞 現 已 同 時 涵 蓋 其 他 物 品 ， 例 如 聯 網 電 腦 系 統 和 其 他 電 腦 科 技 ， 例 如 互 聯 網 ， 流 動 電 訊 和 智 能 卡 。<br />\n<br />\n在 <strong>香 港 現 行 法 例 下 ， 「 電 腦 」</strong> 一 詞 在 《 證 據 條 例 》 （ 第 8 章 ） 第 22A 條 、 《 稅 務 條 例 》 （ 第 112 章 ） 第 26A 條 及 《 商 業 登 記 條 例 》 （ 第 310 章 ） 第 19 條 內 被 界 定 為 ： <strong>「 儲 存 、 處 理 或 檢 索 資 料 的 器 材 」 </strong>。<br />\n<br />\n然 而 ， 《 電 子 交 易 條 例 》 （ 第 553 章 ） 並 無 試 圖 界 定 「 電 腦 」 或 「 電 腦 系 統 」 的 定 義 ， 而 是 採 用 了 「 資 訊 系 統 」 的 概 念 。"},{"pid":"69a2a3aa3788fc6558330c80e684fbce3a8b497b","tid":575830,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T12:27:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap200!zh-Hant-HK/s161\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elegislation.gov.hk%2Fhk%2Fcap200%21zh-Hant-HK%2Fs161&d=g96y2tAFGhmrj%2B%2FMFxWKG9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=8b94fa12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap200!zh-Hant-HK/s161</a><br />\n<br />\n第200章 《刑事罪行條例》 ── 第161條 <br />\n<br />\n有犯罪或不誠實意圖而取用電腦<br />\n<br />\n(1)任何人有下述意圖或目的而取用電腦 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(a)意圖犯罪(不論是在取用電腦的同時或在日後任何時間)；<br />\n(b)<strong>不誠實地意圖欺騙</strong>(不論是在取用電腦的同時或在日後任何時間)；<br />\n(c)目的在於使其本人或他人不誠實地獲益(不論是在取用電腦的同時或在日後任何時間)；或<br />\n(d)<strong>不誠實地意圖導致他人蒙受損失</strong>(不論是在取用電腦的同時或在日後任何時間)，<br />\n即屬犯罪，一經循公訴程序定罪，可處監禁5年。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n某連登仔不誠實使用電腦，男扮女，發出錯誤資訊，令讀者信以為真，引導讀者作出錯誤決定，導致蒙受損失。"},{"pid":"9932d3b16b2d41de4f662f46c3fb571af26b21b3","tid":575830,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T12:28:11.000Z","msg":"或者係精神上受損失都得"},{"pid":"1116accf5fefe1f5672bc8459fc9b1436129b98d","tid":575830,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T12:30:34.000Z","msg":"咪on9 啦，呢條係萬能key, 乜都入硬架啦，你坐喺梳化睇電視乜都唔做佢一樣可以入呢條罪！"},{"pid":"e2a98c1737f1d2ac58c05788ffba8567eb11daeb","tid":575830,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T12:32:38.000Z","msg":"係獎嚟，我之前幾辛苦咁用 SQL Injection 先攞到個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家咁易攞唔得㗎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2eac8e7d7c52577b5fff17943002521ca2cc71e","tid":575830,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2a98c1737f1d2ac58c05788ffba8567eb11daeb","tid":575830,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T12:32:38.000Z","msg":"係獎嚟，我之前幾辛苦咁用 SQL Injection 先攞到個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家咁易攞唔得㗎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T12:33:48.000Z","msg":"唔明"},{"pid":"8543cf293855f6ceca3d9ef37d3e25f0fddb3707","tid":575830,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T12:35:26.000Z","msg":"教埋你嘞怕你唔明，<br />\n<br />\n你生坐喺梳化已經想用條J意圖強奸，但唔告你呢條，告你不誠實使用電腦罪，因你你睇電視，電視有粒microchip, 即係電腦！<br />\n<br />\n罪名係不誠實使用電腦意圖強姦！"},{"pid":"1dfb14ffc10cd823694debc4ddb21f9ee01ada28","tid":575830,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2eac8e7d7c52577b5fff17943002521ca2cc71e","tid":575830,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2a98c1737f1d2ac58c05788ffba8567eb11daeb","tid":575830,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T12:32:38.000Z","msg":"係獎嚟，我之前幾辛苦咁用 SQL Injection 先攞到個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家咁易攞唔得㗎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T12:33:48.000Z","msg":"唔明"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T12:36:32.000Z","msg":"係黑客獎嚟，而家個裁判濫頒獎對我哋依啲好撚唔公平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a629913cd70330e4c2b10135be27dbbc642aba54","tid":575830,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T12:40:12.000Z","msg":"不誠實使用電腦類似thought crime，係好荒謬。"},{"pid":"d4bfc8eacb16c2427892ac5df94acccdd96844c3","tid":575830,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8543cf293855f6ceca3d9ef37d3e25f0fddb3707","tid":575830,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T12:35:26.000Z","msg":"教埋你嘞怕你唔明，<br />\n<br />\n你生坐喺梳化已經想用條J意圖強奸，但唔告你呢條，告你不誠實使用電腦罪，因你你睇電視，電視有粒microchip, 即係電腦！<br />\n<br />\n罪名係不誠實使用電腦意圖強姦！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T12:40:12.000Z","msg":"但有樣叫法律證據<br />\n你的意圖要有證據先得<br />\n最少都要在網上留過言"},{"pid":"6b6002b0a856582f360053739682d68c3c4b7e12","tid":575830,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4bfc8eacb16c2427892ac5df94acccdd96844c3","tid":575830,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8543cf293855f6ceca3d9ef37d3e25f0fddb3707","tid":575830,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T12:35:26.000Z","msg":"教埋你嘞怕你唔明，<br />\n<br />\n你生坐喺梳化已經想用條J意圖強奸，但唔告你呢條，告你不誠實使用電腦罪，因你你睇電視，電視有粒microchip, 即係電腦！<br />\n<br />\n罪名係不誠實使用電腦意圖強姦！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T12:40:12.000Z","msg":"但有樣叫法律證據<br />\n你的意圖要有證據先得<br />\n最少都要在網上留過言"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T12:45:51.000Z","msg":"判得呢條罪仲有臉講法律？"},{"pid":"216ce4295ec770554a56d364415a76cd5836c72d","tid":575830,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T12:49:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/28/204914_51f4f6d4fcc0ed42f267dfb45bee0e15.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F28%2F204914_51f4f6d4fcc0ed42f267dfb45bee0e15.png&h=f4990ce9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/28/204914_377f7666cdc14dca4e76464d5cff335a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F28%2F204914_377f7666cdc14dca4e76464d5cff335a.png&h=8b04fdcb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/28/204916_3c4384fd424eba1e4cce250d99188d97.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F28%2F204916_3c4384fd424eba1e4cce250d99188d97.png&h=583e4bf1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0d38e738ea0e3e4255ce764632d6a00e661d82d7","tid":575830,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"216ce4295ec770554a56d364415a76cd5836c72d","tid":575830,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T12:49:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/28/204914_51f4f6d4fcc0ed42f267dfb45bee0e15.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F28%2F204914_51f4f6d4fcc0ed42f267dfb45bee0e15.png&h=f4990ce9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/28/204914_377f7666cdc14dca4e76464d5cff335a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F28%2F204914_377f7666cdc14dca4e76464d5cff335a.png&h=8b04fdcb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/28/204916_3c4384fd424eba1e4cce250d99188d97.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F28%2F204916_3c4384fd424eba1e4cce250d99188d97.png&h=583e4bf1&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T12:53:51.000Z","msg":"3月11號投票未？<br />\n香港係俾中共食住<br />\n香港主權在中國<br />\n地理又咁靠中國<br />\n香港反共實死硬<br />\n你要反共，除非移民外國<br />\n或者交返俾台灣做"},{"pid":"5ed564604a2252ea6c741d981ecd212fced4cda4","tid":575830,"uid":78473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T17:01:10.000Z","msg":"真名上拉登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}